{"article_id":"uTbOVyDxaocY0a2D","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Cantor tells the House GOP","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"that 'Senate Republicans need to stand strong","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"and fight . '","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"House takes back seat","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Speaker John Boehner told House Republicans Saturday morning","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that his efforts","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to strike a deal with President Barack Obama","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"are at a standstill .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"There is no agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Boehner said in a room in the Capitol Saturday ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and there are no negotiations between House Republicans and the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"since Obama rejected the speaker ' s effort","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to lift the debt ceiling for six weeks and reopen government","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"while setting up a budget negotiating process .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"With that , a familiar dynamic has resurfaced 12 days into the government shutdown and five days before Treasury says","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"the nation runs out of borrowing authority :","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"The pendulum has swung back to Senate Republicans ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"who now look more likely to cut a deal with Obama","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"to end the first government shutdown since 1996 ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and avoid the first default on U.S. debt in history .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"After the news","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that talks between Boehner and Obama have broken down ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"( D-Nev. )","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"emerged on the floor","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to emphasize","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that the nation ' s eyes are firmly fixed on the chamber .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"\" I was happy to see the Republicans engaged in talks with the president , the House Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"That ' s over with .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"It ' s done .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"They ' re not talking anymore , \"","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Reid said .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"\" I say to my friends on the Republican side of this Senate ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"time is running out . \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"House Republicans are , for the first time , acknowledging that reality .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"House Majority Leader Eric Cantor","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"( R-Va. )","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"told the closed meeting of GOP lawmakers","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that , \" Senate Republicans need to stand strong","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and fight , \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"according to sources in the room .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"\" It ' s all good , \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Rep. Raul Labrador","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"( R-Idaho )","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"said .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"\" It ' s now up to the Senate Republicans to stand up . \"","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"House Republican leaders met with Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Friday","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to receive a briefing on the state of play in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Sens . Susan Collins","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"( R-Maine )","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"and Joe Manchin","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"( D-W.Va. )","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"are circulating a 23-page draft bill","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"that would increase the nation ' s borrowing limit through January","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and reopen government until March .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"The bill would also delay Obamacare ' s tax on medical devices for two years ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"while replacing the lost revenue","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"by altering the way","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"pensions are calculated .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"It would give increased autonomy to the heads of federal agencies under the constraints of sequester spending levels","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and provide funding increases for fire suppression , a key item for Sen. John McCain","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"( R-Ariz. ) .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"But the clock is the biggest enemy for all sides .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"It ' s unclear","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"if a deal","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"brokered by the Senate","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"could come together before Thursday ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"when the $ 16.7 trillion debt limit must be boosted ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"according to Treasury Secretary Jack Lew .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"House Republican leadership sources say","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"their offer of a six-week debt limit increase might regain favor","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"if a Senate-brokered deal does not come together before that deadline .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"The House goes out of session Saturday","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"and will return Monday evening .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Obama appeared open to the basic outline of the Collins-Manchin plan ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"though the White House has not formally endorsed it .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"The president told Senate Republicans Friday","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"that the medical device tax is not central to his signature domestic achievement","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"- the Affordable Care Act .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Meanwhile , Reid on Saturday will move forward with a procedural vote","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"to lift the debt ceiling through 2014 with no policy add-ons .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"That vote is not expected to reach the key 60-vote threshold","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"needed","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"to proceed to debate .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"But the legislation may be altered later","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"to reflect any compromise","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"struck in the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Neither Senate proposal","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"- the Democrats ' \" clean \" debt-ceiling increase or the Collins-Manchin framework -","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"seems like it would be popular in the House ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"which has trouble passing its own plans .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Many House GOP conservatives see ending the device tax as going after a \" shiny object \"","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"instead of focusing on truly altering the law ,","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"one conservative Republican told .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Appropriators are angry","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that the government would be funded until March","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"- they would prefer a shorter-term measure ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"to allow lawmakers to cobble together a full 2014 spending package","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"\" We have to see what ' s in it , \"","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"House Majority Whip Kevin McCarthy","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"said in a brief interview .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"\" We have to see what it finally looks like","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"if they can ' t get something . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":211,"left":108,"right":210,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":0,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":210,"left":124,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":3,"right":123,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":117,"right":122,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":111,"right